---

<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container footer-inner">
		<div class="footer-brand">
			<div class="footer-logo">
				<span>☕</span> Coffee Chat
			</div>
			<p class="footer-desc">
				디스코드 서버에서 커피챗 참여자를 자동으로 매칭해주는 오픈소스 봇입니다.
				의미 있는 대화를 연결하여 커뮤니티 문화를 강화합니다.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="footer-columns">
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>기능</h4>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/features">기능 소개</a></li>
					<li><a href="/features#algorithm">매칭 알고리즘</a></li>
					<li><a href="/features#commands">슬래시 명령어</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>문서</h4>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/docs/how-to-join">참여 방법</a></li>
					<li><a href="/docs/schedule">매칭 스케줄</a></li>
					<li><a href="/docs/etiquette">에티켓</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>커뮤니티</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/DaleStudy/coffee"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a
						>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/DaleStudy/coffee/issues"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">이슈 제보</a
						>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/DaleStudy"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">DaleStudy</a
						>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="footer-bottom">
		<div class="container">
			<p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} DaleStudy. MIT License.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		background: #1e293b;
		color: var(--color-text-inverse);
		padding: 4rem 0 0;
	}

	.footer-inner {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 2fr;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.footer-logo {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.footer-desc {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.footer-columns {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.footer-col h4 {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.footer-col ul {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.footer-col a {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.footer-col a:hover {
		color: var(--color-text-inverse);
	}

	.footer-bottom {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding: 1.5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.footer-bottom p {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.footer-columns {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.footer-columns {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
